steps.instruction:
### Prep
- Preheat grill
- Cut tomatoes in half; then cut coarsely 
- Finely chop the basil
- Trim the ends of the eggplant; cut lengthwise into 1/2 inch thick slices


### Steps
1. Coat both sides of eggplant slices with cooking spray
2. Sprinkle with 1 teaspoon of vegetable seasoning
3. Place slices on grill (grill for 3 to 4 minutes on each side)
4. Combine tomatoes, basil, balsamic vinegar, and 1/2 teaspoon vegetable seasoning
5. Place eggplant slices on serving dish
6. Top with tomato mixture
7. Sprinkle with cheese and serve
